  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Actions for schools during the coronavirus outbreak
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">What all schools will need to do during the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak from the start of the autumn term.</p>

  </div>
</div>

