              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-28T19:38:00.000+01:00">28 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated guidance to reflect the actions schools need to take before the start of the autumn term - the changes are described within the document and cover the use of face coverings in schools.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
